Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.60,0:03:26.28,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,皆　聞いてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.60,0:03:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,People listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.00,0:03:32.11,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,エクバターナへ進軍する前に　まずは降りかかる火の粉を払わねばならぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.07,0:03:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Before we go to Ecbatana,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.48,0:03:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,you need to deal with the emerging problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:34.88,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ここでシンドゥラを迎え撃つぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.81,0:03:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We here will repulse sindoor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.28,0:03:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The second prince of the kingdom sindoor, Rajendra
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.34,0:03:54.42,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,おお　冷たい　冷たい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.71,0:03:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How cool.
