Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.49,0:03:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Clear. This is what is called "snow."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:03:59.45,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ラジェンドラ殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.25,0:04:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Rajendra we should have exactly starting this invasion?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.08,0:04:03.48,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,本当に侵攻を開始してしまってよかったのでしょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.60,0:04:05.14,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,何を言う
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.69,0:04:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.25,0:04:10.08,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,パルス国内が混乱している今こそ　絶好の機会であろうが
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.36,0:04:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the situation is precarious in Pars.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.96,0:04:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a great opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.33,0:04:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,As to the situation, then this also applies to our kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.34,0:04:13.80,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,混乱というなら　我が国とてそうでありましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.37,0:04:17.60,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,国王カリカーラ二世陛下がお倒れになった今
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.39,0:04:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, when there was our ruler, His Majesty King II of Karikaly,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.74,0:04:20.20,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下がシンドゥラを留守にされては…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.81,0:04:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince missing in sindoor ...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.45,0:04:21.99,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ガーデーヴィか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.49,0:04:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Gadevi, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:25.08,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ヤツのことなら　気にする必要はない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.48,0:04:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,On it there is no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.57,0:04:27.88,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,何が第一王子だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.58,0:04:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What other first prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.88,0:04:30.74,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,たかが　ひと月ほど早く生まれただけだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.99,0:04:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He was born just a month earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.80,0:04:36.25,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,才能も器量も　どう考えても　俺の方が王としてふさわしい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.83,0:04:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,According to their abilities and skills,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.25,0:04:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter what, and the throne is more suitable for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.37,0:04:37.31,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.42,0:04:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:43.31,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ　パルスの王太子の首を手土産に　王都に凱旋といこうか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.80,0:04:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how about take the head of the Crown Prince Parsis
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.12,0:04:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,as a souvenir on his return to the capital?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:04.91,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.30,0:05:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince.
