Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.34,0:05:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince, we are ready to go into battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.62,0:05:10.57,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,行ってまいります
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.76,0:05:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.68,0:05:11.65,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.86,0:05:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.94,0:05:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Drug ...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.97,0:05:13.54,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あの…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.94,0:05:14.60,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,何か
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.01,0:05:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.42,0:05:18.77,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,私もやはり　出陣した方がよくないか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.47,0:05:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I, too, should go into battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.05,0:05:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.08,0:05:19.74,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.91,0:05:23.85,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,私だけ　ただここで座って待っているのでは　申し訳が立たない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.97,0:05:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm just going to sit here alone and waiting for the break a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.65,0:05:27.82,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,私にも何かできることがあるはずだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I, too, can do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.60,0:05:29.22,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.60,0:05:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.27,0:05:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You are now
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.28,0:05:34.20,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,今やあなたはこのペシャワールの数万の兵を束ねる身
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.52,0:05:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,manages several tens of thousands of people in Peshavarde.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.74,0:05:38.05,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,いちいち御自ら戦場に出られる必要はありません
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.78,0:05:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You do not need to go out on the field every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.37,0:05:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.37,0:05:39.11,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,だが…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.08,0:05:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Count this time on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.11,0:05:41.51,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,今回は我々にお任せください
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.91,0:05:43.91,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,必ずや吉報をお届けしましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.03,0:05:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We will definitely bring you good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.42,0:05:48.88,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,分かった　お主たちのやりやすいようにやってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.50,0:05:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.83,0:05:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Do as you would be easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.31,0:05:54.31,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,まったく　昨日のことを気にされているのかと思えば
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.33,0:05:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I yesterday and thought that it is something disturbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.57,0:05:58.57,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ　それを考えたくもないというのもあろうがな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sure of it, he would not think of.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.20,0:06:03.94,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ座っているだけでは皆に申し訳が立たぬ…か
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.30,0:06:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Said, breaking a promise, if it is to just sit and wait, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.82,0:06:07.40,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,一軍の将の言葉とは思えんな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.82,0:06:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I can not believe that this is the word army commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.77,0:06:10.08,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,本当に心優しいお方だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.85,0:06:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He has a very kind soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.77,0:06:14.08,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,だが　ただ優しいだけでは王にはなれぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.85,0:06:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But a little kindness, to become king.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:15.48,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そうかな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.73,0:06:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.74,0:06:21.54,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ああいうお方だからこそ　我々も兵たちも信じてついていける
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.82,0:06:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It is because he is,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.82,0:06:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,we and other people believe in him and follow him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.48,0:06:25.85,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,一人くらいは　そんな王がいてもいいのではないか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps, at least one can be the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.58,0:06:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.62,0:06:29.48,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,確かにな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.42,0:06:34.48,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ　行くぞ　殿下に吉報をお届けすると約束したからな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.54,0:06:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, we promised to bring good news to Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.57,0:06:43.74,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,アルスラーン…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.63,0:06:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Lions ...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.28,0:06:48.54,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,つくづくヤツの行く先には争いが絶えませぬな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.35,0:06:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,At every step, where he steps,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.68,0:06:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He faced only with strife.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.20,0:06:58.62,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,放っておいてよろしいのですかな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.36,0:06:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We believe that it is necessary to leave it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.02,0:07:05.88,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-1\fs51}ダリューンらが城を離れた今　あの小僧を殺すには絶好の機会かと思われますが
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.15,0:07:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Daryuna and the other in the fortress there,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.65,0:07:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,this is the best opportunity to finally kill the guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.17,0:07:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We go back to Ecbatana.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.17,0:07:08.08,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,エクバターナに戻るぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.34,0:07:11.57,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,いいでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.37,0:07:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.34,0:07:29.85,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,では　作戦どおり　我々は先に行かせてもらうぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.47,0:07:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So, as planned, we will go forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.85,0:07:32.20,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ　よろしく頼む
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.93,0:07:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we count on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.57,0:07:34.91,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ナルサス　聞きたいことがある
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Narsus, I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.31,0:07:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.31,0:07:35.94,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:38.88,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,侵攻してきたシンドゥラの兵は５万
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.27,0:07:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The army sindoor fifty thousand soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.57,0:07:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We also only ten thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.57,0:07:42.05,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,対して　こちらは１万の兵しか出していない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.30,0:07:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.37,0:07:42.82,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.37,0:07:48.00,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,少数の兵で多数の兵を破るというのは　邪道ではなかったか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.49,0:07:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is not it strange to go less against a large army?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:51.17,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,今回はあえて邪道をいくのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.53,0:07:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,At this time, we have deliberately resorted to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.42,0:07:54.51,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ダリューン　お前はかつてセリカで
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.50,0:07:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Daryun you once in Serik
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.57,0:07:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,recognized three principles on which it is worth remembering the war,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.65,0:07:59.94,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,戦いにあたって注意すべき三つの理とは何か　学んだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.92,0:07:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.07,0:08:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,heaven time, the advantage of location, coordination of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.11,0:08:03.48,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,天の時　地の利　人の和
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.11,0:08:05.54,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そういうことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.22,0:08:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.72,0:08:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And sindoor currently violates all three principles.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.74,0:08:09.85,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,シンドゥラは今　その三つの理を全て犯している
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.74,0:08:14.11,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下　夜も更けてまいりました
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.81,0:08:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince, too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.51,0:08:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we break camp somewhere here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.62,0:08:16.94,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,この辺で　ひとまず陣を張るべきでは
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.17,0:08:19.45,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,いや　このまま山を越える
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.17,0:08:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we continue to go through the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.45,0:08:24.94,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし　この寒さで　兵も馬もだいぶ体力を消耗しておりますぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.73,0:08:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But because of this cold and the people and the horses get tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.94,0:08:28.80,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,だからこそ　立ち止まってしまうわけにはいかんのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.01,0:08:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why we can not just sit around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.17,0:08:32.22,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,山を越えればペシャワールの城はすぐそこだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.28,0:08:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon cross the mountains, just go out to Peshavardu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.34,0:08:33.08,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,一気に…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.37,0:08:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And soon ...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.54,0:08:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A-attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.02,0:08:37.88,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,敵襲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.54,0:08:47.88,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,やはり来たか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.59,0:08:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Came the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.97,0:08:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise it would be boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.97,0:08:50.00,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そう来なくては面白くない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,In the attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:50.92,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,かかれ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.17,0:09:01.62,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,まずは　三つの理の一つ　天の時
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.19,0:09:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,To begin with the first principle:
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.31,0:09:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,heaven time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.08,0:09:04.94,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,シンドゥラ兵は常夏の南国育ち
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.15,0:09:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Soldiers sindoor grown in the south, where eternal summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.08,0:09:08.85,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,真冬の雪山で果たしてどこまで戦えるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.11,0:09:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,In the snow-covered mountains in winter
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.70,0:09:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,how well they can fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.25,0:09:20.42,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,シンドゥラの蛮族ども　この双刀将軍キシュワードが相手になってやるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.44,0:09:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sindoor barbarians!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.71,0:09:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I Kisvard General two swords, your opponent!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.30,0:09:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.37,0:09:27.05,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ひるむな　シンドゥラの武勇　パルスの兵どもに見せつけてやれ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.17,0:09:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Show all soldiers Parsis valor sindoor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.14,0:09:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Next area.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.14,0:09:32.82,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そして　地の利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.89,0:09:39.51,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,来たか　ダリューン
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.94,0:09:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Daruna!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.61,0:09:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Attacked from both sides! Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.62,0:09:41.71,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,挟み撃ちだ　退け
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.94,0:09:47.51,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,パルスは彼らにとって未知の土地　こちらは細かい地形まで把握済みだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.02,0:09:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They do not know Parsa district.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.94,0:09:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And we are familiar with its topography.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.78,0:09:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So Daryun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.80,0:09:50.22,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ　ダリューン
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:52.82,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ヤシャスィーン
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.99,0:09:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Jasasuiin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.62,0:10:03.65,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,押し返せ　それでもシンドゥラの男か
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.67,0:10:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Pushes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.87,0:10:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You people sindoor or anyone ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.74,0:10:12.05,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,力任せに押し返そうとは…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.93,0:10:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They are trying to push the main force?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.20,0:10:14.37,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なんと傲岸な将だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.26,0:10:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What an arrogant general!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.42,0:10:23.14,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,甘かったな　俺の兵たちがこんな奇襲程度でひるむものかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.52,0:10:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not underestimate us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.19,0:10:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,My people will never yield to a surprise attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.57,0:10:29.80,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-1}天の時　地の利を犯してまで攻め込んでくるだけの自信はあるということか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.61,0:10:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's confident enough in the invasion,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.61,0:10:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,though time is against heaven and benefits area.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.07,0:10:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But what about the rest of coherence of people?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.08,0:10:33.71,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,だが　残る人の和は　どうかな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.77,0:10:35.57,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,このまま押せ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.91,0:10:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Continue to press!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.70,0:10:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Come from behind ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.85,0:10:38.28,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,背後からだと
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.20,0:10:48.50,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,また新手か
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.21,0:10:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Reinforcement?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.65,0:10:50.91,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,いや　この音はシンドゥラの
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.67,0:10:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it sounds sindoor ...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.91,0:10:54.08,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,み…見ろ　あの旗印は…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.01,0:10:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,C-look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.47,0:10:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This banner ...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.54,0:10:57.22,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ガ…ガーデーヴィ殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.68,0:10:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Prince Gadevi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.57,0:10:59.62,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ　第一王子の軍が
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.82,0:11:02.20,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,え…援軍に来てくれたのでは
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.89,0:11:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,H-probably, come to our aid ...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.57,0:11:09.65,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ち…違う　ガーデーヴィ殿下は敵だ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.69,0:11:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,N-no! Prince Gadevi our enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.71,0:11:12.80,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,大変です
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.74,0:11:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We have problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.78,0:11:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.85,0:11:13.82,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なんの騒ぎだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.07,0:11:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,According to the report, Prince Gadevi leads a huge army
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.08,0:11:16.40,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ガーデーヴィ王子が大軍を引き連れ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.54,0:11:19.85,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,我が軍の後尾に襲いかかってきた由にございます
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.37,0:11:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and attack us from the rear!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.83,0:11:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Can not be!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.85,0:11:20.68,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,バカな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.91,0:11:24.16,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,俺がここにいることは　ガーデーヴィはまだ知らぬはず
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.96,0:11:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Gadevi should know that I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.48,0:11:29.91,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あるいは　此度の我々の行動　全てひそかに監視されていたのでは
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.54,0:11:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Or perhaps they secretly watched our every move.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It can not be!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.11,0:11:30.82,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,まさか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.06,0:11:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You go around to the left!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.09,0:11:48.10,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,左に回れ　背後からガーデーヴィの兵が迫ってきてるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.40,0:11:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Gadevi people approaching from behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.82,0:11:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? Left!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.85,0:11:54.51,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,何をしている　左だ　前に出たら　パルス兵に殺されるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.78,0:11:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If you leave ahead, you will be killed parsiantsy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.33,0:12:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Though the night and moon,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.42,0:12:04.17,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,新月の夜とはいえ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.33,0:12:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,certainly, the soldiers are stupid,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.34,0:12:09.60,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,通常なら　女　子供の声にだまされるような愚かな兵でもないだろうが
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.42,0:12:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,to distinguish the voices of women and children.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.37,0:12:15.08,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,シンドゥラは現在　二人の王子による世継ぎ争いの真っただ中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.42,0:12:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But sindoor now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.80,0:12:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,a battle between the two princes of the right of inheritance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.77,0:12:19.08,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,意識せずとも　兵たちの心にも不安はあろう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.89,0:12:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe they do not know,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.93,0:12:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,but in the hearts of the soldiers hidden anxiety.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.34,0:12:22.74,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そこをつけば　崩れるのはあっという間だ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.43,0:12:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If they hit, they quickly break down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:25.00,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,これが人の和か
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.31,0:12:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This coherence of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.60,0:12:28.05,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そろそろ　例の場所に近づきつつある
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.69,0:12:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,They are gradually approaching the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.57,0:12:31.65,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,頃合いだな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.65,0:12:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.22,0:12:37.25,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ　５万と１万の戦力差　今ひっくり返してみせよう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.32,0:12:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus, the difference between fifty and ten thousand
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.20,0:12:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It will now be refuted!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.03,0:12:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.94,0:12:51.37,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだ　この音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.96,0:12:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.88,0:12:58.22,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,こ…これは　まさか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.30,0:12:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, it's ...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.47,0:12:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Can not be!..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.05,0:13:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Get out of here! Here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.05,0:13:03.00,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,走れ　ここから離れろ　ここは…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.42,0:13:09.48,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そう　そこは凍った湖の上さ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.52,0:13:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. This is the top of a frozen lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.87,0:13:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I still see a nightmare?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.97,0:13:24.94,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は悪夢でも見ているのか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.60,0:13:28.85,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ラジェンドラ王子に急ぎ申し上げたきことあり
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.66,0:13:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an urgent message for Prince Rajendra!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.11,0:13:30.54,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下はおわすや
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.17,0:13:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.80,0:13:33.62,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ラシェンドラはここにいる　何が起こった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.90,0:13:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Rajendra here! What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.84,0:13:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Daryun, this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.85,0:13:35.85,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ダリューン　この男だ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.51,0:13:37.31,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.59,0:13:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.94,0:13:48.57,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,悪いが　捕虜となっていただこう　ラジェンドラ王子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.95,0:13:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I'll have to take you prisoner, Prince Rajendra!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.82,0:14:00.31,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,次に会ったら　生かしてはおかんぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:14:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,In following our meeting I will not leave alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.34,0:14:16.37,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,動くと死ぬよ　シンドゥラの色男
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.38,0:14:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Dvineshsya, and you're dead, sinduriysky handsome.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.22,0:14:30.48,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,いや　参った　参った
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.81,0:14:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I caught, caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.48,0:14:32.42,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,見事にしてやられたわ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.49,0:14:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Brilliantly outmaneuvered.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.01,0:14:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The Alfred, you are good to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.02,0:14:35.31,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,アルフリード　よくやってくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.48,0:14:40.05,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,いえ　ナルサス卿の策がよろしきを得たからにございます
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.54,0:14:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.54,0:14:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all thanks to the magnificent trick Mr. Narsusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.77,0:14:55.17,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,聞いてはいたが　こんなにかわいい大将だったか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.80,0:14:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard, but did not know that their leader is so small.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.39,0:14:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what will you do with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.40,0:14:58.17,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,で　俺をどうするつもりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.45,0:15:01.54,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,見せしめに兵の前で処刑でもするかい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.48,0:15:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Penalty in front of my people, for the edification?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.31,0:15:04.42,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ラジェンドラ殿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.40,0:15:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Rajendra I, Crown Prince Parsis, Arslan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.97,0:15:08.68,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,私はパルスの王太子　アルスラーンと申します
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.25,0:15:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We treated a little roughly,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.31,0:15:13.00,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,いささか乱暴でしたが　お話ししたいことがあって
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.24,0:15:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,but I would like to discuss with you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.99,0:15:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,your appearance here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.00,0:15:14.88,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,このようにご招待いたしました
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.88,0:15:17.20,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ほう　驚いたな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.86,0:15:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.20,0:15:21.45,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,パルスでは　縄で縛って引っ立てることを招待と言うのか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.25,0:15:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The Pars binding and transport of person called an invitation?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.88,0:15:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,For this I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.91,0:15:24.68,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,これは　大変失礼しました
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.10,0:15:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to talk to you on equal terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.11,0:15:39.85,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,これで対等にお話しできるかと思いますが
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.91,0:15:44.57,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ　いいだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.98,0:15:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,OK then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.71,0:15:47.60,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,聞いてやらんこともない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.73,0:15:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I did not say that it is not heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.11,0:16:02.02,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,辺境の地ゆえ　大したおもてなしもできませんが
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.20,0:15:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,on the border
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.75,0:16:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,not much you can regale guests, but ...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.08,0:16:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.11,0:16:03.25,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,頂こう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.62,0:16:10.22,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,おお　いやいや　この酒はなかなかいけるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.89,0:16:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No no. This wine is pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.37,0:16:12.40,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,シンドゥラにはない味わいだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.37,0:16:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Such taste sindoor not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.88,0:16:16.85,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ　皆も大いに食べ　飲んでくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.89,0:16:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we also have a drink to the dregs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.25,0:16:30.68,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,それにしても　まだ子供と聞いていたが　先刻は見事な采配だった
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.31,0:16:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But still,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.73,0:16:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,though I have heard that you are still a child,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.40,0:16:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,but your command was terrific.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.66,0:16:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I am amazed Prince Arslan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.71,0:16:35.54,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,感服したぞ　アルスラーン王子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.77,0:16:38.45,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,いえ　私は何もしておりませぬよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.83,0:16:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I did not do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.45,0:16:42.77,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,仲間たちに助けられてばかりです
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.46,0:16:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I only come to the rescue comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.54,0:16:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Not subordinates and comrades?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.54,0:16:48.94,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,臣下ではなく　仲間か　つくづく面白い男だな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.75,0:16:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You are a very interesting person.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, come on! And you drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.94,0:16:50.94,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,さあさあ　お主も　飲め飲め
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.68,0:16:53.17,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ…　はい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.53,0:16:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.85,0:16:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I keep you company.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.88,0:16:58.22,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたのお相手は私がしよう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.85,0:17:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.85,0:17:00.88,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,おお　それはいい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.91,0:17:04.82,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,おっと　俺も交ぜてもらおうか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.93,0:17:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well. Allow me to join.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:08.65,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,酒の肴に楽士の詩はどうだい　王子様
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.06,0:17:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the music of the singer to the wine, the prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.65,0:17:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting. Then, make a little competition?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.65,0:17:12.31,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,面白い　ならば　飲み比べといこうじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.97,0:17:22.22,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ああっ　いや…　あぁ…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.70,0:17:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.71,0:17:27.17,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,本当に二人ともよくやってくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.75,0:17:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You are a very good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.54,0:17:28.91,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがとうございます
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.59,0:17:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Many thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.11,0:17:34.00,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ　あの程度の任務　私一人で十分だったんだけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.12,0:17:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, such a mission ...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I would and she coped.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.20,0:17:38.20,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,お前こそ引っ込んでてもらって結構だったさ　出しゃばり女
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.30,0:17:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Just can cope without you, obsessive woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.20,0:17:42.20,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なっ…　出しゃばりって何よ　あんたの方がよっぽど出しゃばりじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.76,0:17:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean an obsession?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.35,0:17:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You yourself everywhere thrusting his nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:44.82,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,私はナルサスと話してるんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.43,0:17:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm talking to Narsusom!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.06,0:17:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You can even now get along a little bit, guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.11,0:17:51.22,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなときぐらい　仲よくできないのか　お前たち
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.20,0:18:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Heck...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.22,0:18:07.08,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ちくしょう　頭の中で水牛の群れが合唱しながら踊ってやがるぅ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.91,0:18:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,In my head I am singing in unison and even dancing herd unruly oxen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.17,0:18:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,With such secretly get drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.22,0:18:13.71,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,この俺が酔い潰せぬとは　侮れんなぁ　パルスの女
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.46,0:18:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Women Parsis directly from steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.76,0:18:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.77,0:18:16.82,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,おお　失礼した　さあ　もう一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.38,0:18:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So, for another.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.80,0:18:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And, well, uh ...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.82,0:18:17.91,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ　あっ　いや…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.91,0:18:18.88,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ラジェンドラ殿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.93,0:18:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Rajendra.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.97,0:18:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yes, Prince Arslan, how can I help?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.85,0:18:21.74,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,アルスラーン王子　なんですかな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.14,0:18:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's continue our conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.14,0:18:24.20,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,先ほどの話の続きを
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.37,0:18:26.71,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,おうおう　もちろんです
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.43,0:18:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes! Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.25,0:18:31.22,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,話…　そういえば　なんの話だったか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.27,0:18:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Conversation...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.94,0:18:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, what we talked about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.54,0:18:38.45,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたと同盟を結びたい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.57,0:18:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to join with you in a union.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.53,0:18:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,ABOUT...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.57,0:18:40.40,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ほう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.88,0:18:50.05,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,聞こうか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.92,0:18:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.32,0:18:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,First, we will help you ascend to the throne sindoor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.37,0:18:56.02,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-1.5\fs48}まず\h我々は\hあなたがシンドゥラの王位につけるよう\hお手伝いしてさしあげましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.14,0:19:00.14,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そのかわり　お主の戦にも力を貸せと
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.17,0:18:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And in return you want me to help you in your war?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.51,0:19:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.51,0:19:01.14,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ええ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.71,0:19:03.78,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,悪い話ではないと思いますが
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.76,0:19:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the deal is pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.77,0:19:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I would say, it's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.78,0:19:07.34,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,面白いことを言う
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.85,0:19:11.14,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,国を追われた王子に何ができるというのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.85,0:19:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What a prince, banished from his own kingdom?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.34,0:19:12.25,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだと…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.36,0:19:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.27,0:19:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, the prince Rajendra, you do not want to say so,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.28,0:19:14.80,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ですが　ラジェンドラ殿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.05,0:19:20.02,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,こういってはなんですが　今の御身のお立場をよく考えていただきたい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.94,0:19:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like you to think about your current situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.25,0:19:21.97,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,脅迫のつもりか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.28,0:19:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That is a threat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.28,0:19:27.54,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の身に何かあってみろ　俺の兵たちは決して貴様らを許しはしないぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.33,0:19:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I try to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.33,0:19:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,My people so that you will not leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.77,0:19:29.74,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな野蛮なことはいたしません
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.79,0:19:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not resort to such measures.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.05,0:19:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.08,0:19:35.08,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ええ　というか　すでにシンドゥラ国内には通達してしまいました
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.25,0:19:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Or rather, we have alerted people in sindoor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.30,0:19:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.37,0:19:36.05,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,何を
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.84,0:19:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince and Crown Prince Rajendra Parsa, Arslan,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.85,0:19:41.28,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ラシェンドラ王子はパルス国のアルスラーン王太子との間に
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.48,0:19:45.60,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,友誼と正義に基づく盟約を結んだ…とね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.51,0:19:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We created a union based on friendship and honesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.60,0:19:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-what ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.60,0:19:46.85,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なっ　なんだと
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.72,0:19:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And the prince,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.85,0:19:50.05,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,更に　王子はシンドゥラ国に平和をもたらすため
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.98,0:19:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,which will bring peace to the kingdom sindoor,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.37,0:19:54.08,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,国都ウライユールへ進撃を開始した…とも
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.39,0:19:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,already moved into the royal Uraiyur capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.65,0:19:59.71,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様ら　俺を反逆者に仕立て上げようというのか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.69,0:19:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you! ..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.15,0:19:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to make me a traitor?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.94,0:20:06.35,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-1.5\fs50}もとより　いずれ第一王子ガーデーヴィとは雌雄を決するおつもりだったのでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.99,0:20:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You from the beginning is conceived
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.41,0:20:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,to fight Gadevi, the first prince, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.57,0:20:09.34,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,それが少し早まっただけのことですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.62,0:20:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It just happens a little earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.57,0:20:16.48,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,私はあなたをガーデーヴィ王子との交渉に使いたくはない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.62,0:20:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not want to use you in negotiations with Prince Gadevi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.18,0:20:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You have caught me, Crown Prince of Parsis.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.20,0:20:32.20,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,やってくれたな　パルスの王太子よ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.71,0:20:34.31,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,協力していただけますか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.73,0:20:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I count on the cooperation?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.80,0:20:37.80,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,いいだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.82,0:20:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.62,0:20:43.68,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,このラジェンドラがお主に力を貸してやる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.70,0:20:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Rajendra, support you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.16,0:20:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Fate Arslan turned in an unexpected direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.17,0:20:50.34,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,アルスラーンの運命は再び思わぬ方向へと回りはじめた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.58,0:20:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The era of Parsis, December 320 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.60,0:20:54.71,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,パルス暦３２０年１２月
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.11,0:21:00.45,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-1\fs53}アルスラーンはマルズバーン・キシュワードにペシャワール城塞の守護を任せ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.13,0:21:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ostaviv oʙoronu kreposti Peşavarda Marzʙanu Kisvardu,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.71,0:21:05.22,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ラジェンドラ軍と共にシンドゥラを目指して　出陣を決めた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.76,0:21:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Arslan went to accompany the army Rajendra
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.84,0:21:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,in sindoor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.08,0:21:11.77,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,彼がいざなう先に何が待つのか　幼き王子はまだ知る由もない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.10,0:21:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What awaited them at the end of this road?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.64,0:21:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The young prince did not know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.57,0:21:16.68,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,どうだ　アルスラーン殿　俺の自慢の兵たちは
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.64,0:21:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Prince Arslan, about my people, I'm proud?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.94,0:21:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope we will be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.97,0:21:18.68,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,よろしく頼むぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.11,0:21:26.05,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あの男　本当に信用していいものか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.19,0:21:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.65,0:21:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We can definitely trust him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.42,0:21:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,YakuSub Studio
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.36,0:21:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,kimi ga deatta kokoro wa kitto
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.36,0:21:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,All the souls that you could meet on the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.37,0:21:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,translation Mu_Cool
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.15,0:21:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,hitotsu datte machigai janai
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.15,0:21:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,certainly it was pure and innocent,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.37,0:21:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Editorial Mu_Cool
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.33,0:21:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,onaji yume wo daite
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.33,0:21:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We kept the same dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.50,0:21:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Making Helge
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.55,0:21:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,michi wo tagaeta hito wo omotta
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.55,0:21:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,People walking different paths,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.00,0:22:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,nozarashi no akogare wo kakagete susumu kouya
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.00,0:22:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,killed all my hopes and desires revive again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.76,0:22:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,hohoemi mo sono namida mo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.76,0:22:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Smile on his face, tears running down her cheeks,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.47,0:22:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,koko ni suteteyukenai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.47,0:22:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to go ahead, they should not be forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.53,0:22:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,kage wo daite shiroku takaku
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.53,0:22:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Covered by the shadow of the summer, so white and immense,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.64,0:22:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,namonaki boku to kimi no hata
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.64,0:22:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,our with you nameless flag flies.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.91,0:22:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,mada hatenaku tsudzuku kono mich ino kanata ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.91,0:22:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There, on the road, which extends an endless path,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.78,0:22:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,tatta hitotsu no hikari wo sen no kokoro ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.78,0:22:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There is one bright light, and with it a thousand souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.10,0:22:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,miageru sora wo shinjiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.10,0:22:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe in the sky above his head,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.51,0:22:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,michibiku hoshi wo higashi no takami ni sashishimesu yo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.51,0:22:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,there putevodnaâ our star in the east, ee do not engage.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.43,0:22:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,yume wa kono te de kanaeru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.43,0:22:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And their cherished dream in flesh forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.26,0:23:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Royal capital Uraiyur Kingdom sindoor
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.77,0:23:10.57,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,愚かな弟だとは思っていたが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.84,0:23:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought the younger brother a fool, but ...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.37,0:23:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Crown Prince vermilion, Gdevi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.55,0:23:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But at the Pars ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.57,0:23:15.79,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,まさか　パルスと…　アルスラーンなどという小僧と手を組むとは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.60,0:23:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with such a kid as Arlsan!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.52,0:23:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that no matter what happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.54,0:23:23.31,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-1}どうあっても　殿下の王位継承を認めるつもりはないということでしょうな
